data.description: Welcome to this charming, move-in ready single-family home located in the wonderful quiet neighborhood of Forestdale. With 2418 square feet, 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, 3 living spaces, office or mudroom and bonus room/safe room, this property offers ample space for comfortable living. It presents a fantastic opportunity for those looking to add their personal touch and make it their own.
